Z","msg":"拉人好鬆手，但水砲車周圍鳩射"},{"pid":"7e8f7beef0c67142f30855b4802c2a52e5e3b0d1","tid":1665013,"uid":111006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T11:58:34.000Z","msg":"克制？射鳩清真寺水洗都唔清啦<br />\n近距離面對面用槍指嚇記者"},{"pid":"3fdcef162aeaa74ea778bdafe63fbc9c09ceeaeb","tid":1665013,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T11:58:53.000Z","msg":"唔覺"},{"pid":"acb1195e39b669052c2b1ac89f40a09bbf197841","tid":1665013,"uid":310193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T11:58:59.000Z","msg":"仲有清真寺單野喎？<br />\n嗱我唔理，我而家係twitter煲緊，點都要煲大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e3695c896ac7f9b4e5f3e13bfdf2d0dcb14265","tid":1665013,"uid":205099,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:00:02.000Z","msg":"林鄭：不容忍違法暴力 包括警察<br />\n<br />\n有聽眾致電稱，有年輕人被警察「扑爆頭」，批評警方濫暴。林太說：「有live片段，讓人感覺好似過咗火位。」被問會否譴責警方使用過火的暴力，她說要經客觀調查，了解整個執法過程，不能單靠一個畫面。她說：「特區政府不會容忍任何違法行為，不會容忍任何暴力行為，包括警察。我們對於任何暴力行為，都會予以譴責，無論施暴者是什麼背景，什麼政治立場，什麼身分。」林太另接受商台《政經星期六》訪問時亦說自己支持警隊嚴正執法，但不等於「我盲撐每一位警務人員，每一個行動」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20191020/s00001/1571508056340/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%B9%E5%BF%8D%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B-%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191020%2Fs00001%2F1571508056340%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E5%25BF%258D%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B-%25E5%258C%2585%25E6%258B%25AC%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjdVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=34eb829d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191020%2Fs00001%2F1571508056340%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E5%25BF%258D%25E9%2581%25